THIRD-PARTY CONTENT

The MIT license above covers the wrapper source code in this repository
(HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Dockerfile, nginx config, scripts, README, design
assets created for this project).

It does NOT cover the SWF animation files under `public/swf/`. Those files
are © Anatomický ústav 1. LF UK (Institute of Anatomy, 1st Faculty of
Medicine, Charles University in Prague), authored by dr. Brabec, doc. Naňka,
dr. Němcová and prof. Petrovický (2007–2012, FRVŠ projects). They are
mirrored from <https://anat.lf1.cuni.cz/materialy/drahyCNS.zip>.

For redistribution rights, classroom use, or modifications of the SWF
content, contact the Institute directly. This repository serves only as an
unofficial mirror to keep the materials playable after Adobe Flash
deprecation, with no claim to the underlying rights.
